\par\par \uc2 NATIONAL NEWS\par \b \uc2 PANCASILA LIBERATES INDONESIA FROM DEPENDENCE ON FOREIGN PARTIES\b0\par\par\uc2 298 \uc2 words\par \uc2 1 June 2024\par \uc2 LKBN ANTARA\par \uc2 ANTARA\par \uc2 English\par \uc2 Copyright 2024. LKBN Antara \par \par \uc2 By Kenzu Tandiah\par \par \uc2 Jakarta (ANTARA) - President Joko Widodo (Jokowi) emphasized that Pancasila liberates the Indonesian nation from dependence on foreign parties.\par \par \uc2 The head of state made the remark as ceremony inspector during the Pancasila Commemoration Day in Dumai, Riau, on Saturday.\par \par \uc2 "The presence of Pancasila serves as a liberator from our dependence on foreign parties," Jokowi stated, as monitored from here through the Presidential Secretariat"s \uc2 YouTube\uc2  live broadcast.\par \par \uc2 He remarked that Indonesian people should be grateful, as Indonesia remains strong, stable, and united as well as has a growing \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  in the midst of a world full of \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainties\b0 \highlight\uc2  and crises.\par \par \uc2 Amid geopolitical tensions and rivalries, Jokowi urged the people of the nation to remain optimistic, as they can follow Pancasila that leads the nation"s direction.\par \par \uc2 "(It is) because we have solid social and cultural resources. We have human resources and abundant natural resources. Therefore, we must continue to strengthen the nation"s independence in the \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2 ," he explained.\par \par \uc2 He emphasized that Indonesia has consistently pursued a free and active foreign \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  and fought for world peace.\par \par \uc2 Jokowi highlighted Indonesia"s growing role in international politics, as reflected by having successfully hosted the G20 and helmed the ASEAN chairmanship.\par \par \uc2 He affirmed that Indonesia will continue to contribute to the world, including through the recently held World Water Forum (WWF).\par \par \uc2 "Activities in the international arena do not diminish our struggle to be independent in the \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  field. We continue to strive for \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  independence, including through industrialization in the country and downstreaming in various sectors," he explained.\par \par \uc2 Jokowi underscored the need for Indonesia to actively utilize its strategic assets for the welfare of the people.\par \par \uc2 (T.KR-KZU/B/A063/A063) 01-06-2024 12:52:10\par \par \uc2 Document ANTARA0020240601ek610002u\par }\page {\par\fs20\uc2 News\par \b \uc2 Jokowi Calls for Global Peace and Reclamation of Strategic Assets on Pancasila Day\b0\par\par\uc2 584 \uc2 words\par \uc2 1 June 2024\par \uc2 The Jakarta Globe\par \uc2 JGLOBE\par \uc2 English\par \uc2 Copyright 2024. PT Jakarta Globe Media. \par \par \uc2 Riau. President \uc2 Joko "Jokowi" Widodo\uc2  underscored the importance of Indonesia's foundational ideology, Pancasila, in liberating the nation from foreign dependence. He also called for global peace, especially for Palestine, and urged the reclaiming of strategic national assets from foreign control.\par \par \uc2 This message was conveyed during the Pancasila Day ceremony at Garuda Field, Pertamina Hulu Rokan, Dumai, Riau, on Saturday.\par \par \uc2 "We hope that Pancasila will liberate us from dependence on foreign parties," Jokowi said.\par \par \uc2 During the ceremony, Jokowi wore traditional black Teluk Belanga attire adorned with gold patterns, accompanied by a songket cloth and a yellow sash, with a tengkolok or tanjak headpiece. Meanwhile, ministers uniformly wore traditional Riau clothing.\par \par \uc2 According to Jokowi, Pancasila plays a significant role in maintaining Indonesia's unity and stability, positively impacting Indonesia and serving as an example for other nations.\par \par \uc2 Pancasila consists of five principles representing Indonesia's national ideology: belief in one God, a just and civilized humanity, national unity, democracy, and social justice.\par \par \uc2 In a tense geopolitical climate and \b \highlight22\uc2 economic uncertainties\b0 \highlight\uc2 , the head of state urged all Indonesians to remain optimistic, highlighting Pancasila as the nation's guiding principle.\par \par \uc2 "We have strong social and cultural capital, quality human resources, and abundant natural resources. Therefore, we must continue to strengthen our national independence and \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  self-reliance," he explained.\par \par \uc2 Jokowi reaffirmed Indonesia's consistent independent and active foreign \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2 , advocating for the independence of all nations, including Palestine, and supporting world peace.\par \par \uc2 He also noted Indonesia's growing role in international politics, evidenced by its leadership in the G-20, successful ASEAN chairmanship, and contributions to various international events, including the recently concluded World Water Forum (WWF) Summit.\par \par \uc2 "Active participation in international affairs does not diminish our fight for \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  self-reliance. We continue to strive for \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  independence through domestic industrialization in various sectors," he added.\par \par \uc2 The President stressed that the nation's wealth must be fully utilized for the people's prosperity and that Indonesia must actively reclaim strategic national assets for management and maximum benefit for its citizens.\par \par \uc2 One significant national asset successfully reclaimed is the Rokan Oil Block in Riau.\par \par \uc2 "After taking over the majority shares of (gold mine)Freeport, we then took over the Rokan Block in Dumai, the most productive oil and gas block in Indonesia's history, previously managed by Caltex and \uc2 Chevron\uc2  for 97 years," he asserted.\par \par \uc2 Jokowi reported that state oil and gas company \uc2 Pertamina\uc2 's current production in the Rokan Block reaches 162,000 barrels per day, higher than when managed by Caltex or \uc2 Chevron\uc2 , contributing 25 percent of Indonesia's total national production.\par \par \uc2 "The Rokan Block is the largest. Freeport and the Rokan Block are just examples of our spirit and efforts to achieve political sovereignty and \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  independence, embodying Pancasila in real life, building an \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  that stands on our strength and serves national interests," he explained.\par \par \uc2 The President also encouraged the actualization and transmission of Pancasila's values amidst rapid developments. These values need to be manifested through concrete actions and policies, producing clear results for the people's benefit.\par \par \uc2 However, Jokowi also suggested that the methods of transmitting Pancasila's values should be adapted to the younger generation, which currently dominates Indonesia's demographics. Future generations, including millennials, Gen Z, and Alpha, are expected to uphold Indonesia's cultural heritage.\par \par \uc2 "Therefore, we must educate Pancasila in their ways, with exemplary practices, and use and develop Indonesian culture," Jokowi concluded.\par \par \uc2 Document JGLOBE0020240601ek6100006\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
