nal shocks and boost its growth. It urged the next administration to maintain such \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal\b0 \highlight\uc2  prudence.\par \par \uc2 "We see Indonesia as one of the few countries that have implemented a simple \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal\b0 \highlight\uc2  rule that everyone understands and has done so consistently over the past several years," Wael Mansour, a senior economist at the \uc2 World Bank\uc2 , said at a press briefing on June 19.\par \par \uc2 "This has enabled markets to deem it a credible anchor to attract investment and lower the risk premium," he continued.\par \par \uc2 The \uc2 World Bank\uc2  found that some of Prabowo's campaign promises could benefit human capital development, such as the free lunch program, but it also cautioned that those initiatives should be put in place gradually and in a fiscally sound manner.\par \par \uc2 The bank also offered several recommendations in its latest Indonesia \b \highlight22\uc2 Economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  Prospects report in June.\par \par \uc2 These included improving revenue by expanding the number of entities designated as taxable entrepreneurs, removing \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  exemptions that did not benefit the poor and improving use of data to verify people's incomes, among many others.\par \par \uc2 On \b \highlight22\uc2 spending\b0 \highlight\uc2 , the \uc2 World Bank\uc2  suggested the government reallocate resources from less effective programs, such as such as energy \b \highlight22\uc2 subsidies\b0 \highlight\uc2 , to better-targeted direct social aid, arguing that this would free up \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal\b0 \highlight\uc2  room for other, higher-priority expenditures, even though it would require complex reforms.\par \par \uc2 "Some households may be affected by the increase in fuel prices but are not part of the social protection programs. This requires updated targeting mechanisms to ensure that eligible households are included in social protection programs," Habib Rab, the \uc2 World Bank\uc2 's lead economist for Indonesia and Timor-Leste, explained on the same occasion.\par \par \uc2 The \uc2 International Monetary Fund\uc2  also offered similar counsel, saying the country's "hard-earned" \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  credibility should be preserved.\par \par \uc2 "Indonesia's 3 percent of GDP \b \highlight22\uc2 deficit\b0 \highlight\uc2  cap remains well-suited to support its Golden Vision [for 2045], especially if supported by a strengthening of \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal\b0 \highlight\uc2  revenues to boost development \b \highlight22\uc2 spending\b0 \highlight\uc2 ," said Maria Gonzalez, the \uc2 IMF\uc2 's mission chief to Indonesia, in a statement on June 14.\par \par \uc2 She also pointed out that the narrower \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal deficit\b0 \highlight\uc2  last year, anchored by the first primary surplus in about a decade, had preserved \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  space for this year and next year's expansionary \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal\b0 \highlight\uc2  stance.\par \par \uc2 Fikri C. Permana, an economist at KB Valbury Sekuritas, welcomed the Prabowo team's clarification of the incoming administration's \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal\b0 \highlight\uc2  intentions but said the market was still cautiously awaiting clarity on the people who would be tasked with handling government finances.\par \par \uc2 "The market is really worried about \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2  right now. Thus, a negative sentiment could make everything look grey," Fikri told The Jakarta Post on Monday.\par \par \uc2 He said the rupiah could bounce back to between Rp 15,800 and Rp 16,100 per dollar by the end of the year, strengthening from this month's level of around Rp 16,400 per dollar.\par \par \uc2 He said the improvement would be driven by the market anticipating the finalization the 2025 state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  and the waning of external pressure as the \uc2 US Federal Reserve\uc2  became clearer about its planned rate cut.\par \par \uc2 Document JKPOST0020240624ek6p00001\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
