o stated that there was no interference by Jokowi, although it issued an ethical note regarding Prabowo-Gibran's victory.\par \par \uc2 In his remarks in Senayan this morning, Jokowi underlined the need for the government to boost global competitiveness to maintain \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  and political stability. The former Jakarta governor said he hoped to achieve structural reform by simplifying procedures. "To be more efficient and result-oriented," he said\par \par \uc2 Jokowi also asked for support from all components of the nation to maintain sustainability to bring progress to the country and hopes for a smooth transition process.\par \par \uc2 President Jokowi will be replaced by Gerindra chairman and Defense Minister \uc2 Prabowo Subianto\uc2  in October 2024. The former Solo mayor is confident that the new administration led by Prabowo will pay serious attention to the BPK's recommendations, just as he did in his years in office.\par \par \uc2 DANIEL A. FAJRI\par \par \uc2 Editor's Choice: Jokowi Inaugurates Pamukkulu Dam Project Worth Rp1.6 trillion in South Sulawesi\par \par \uc2 Click here to get the latest news updates from Tempo on Google News\par \par {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://statik.tempo.co/data/2024/07/03/id_1315811/1315811_720.jpg"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 Click here to view picture}}}\par \par \uc2 Document TEMPOE0020240708ek78000b5\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
