\par\par \b \uc2 The  \highlight22\uc2 budget \highlight\uc2  is yours, Prabowo\b0\par\par\uc2 682 \uc2 words\par \uc2 19 August 2024\par \uc2 The Jakarta Post\par \uc2 JKPOST\par 6\par \uc2 English\par \uc2 (c) 2024 The Jakarta Post \par \par \uc2 The Jakarta Post,\par \par \uc2 The 2025 draft \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  is here, and this will be president-elect \uc2 Prabowo Subianto\uc2 's first. The plan drawn up by President \uc2 Joko "Jokowi" Widodo\uc2 's administration sticks to the safety bounds prescribed by the State Finances Law, which limits the \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal deficit\b0 \highlight\uc2  to no more than 3 percent of gross domestic product (GDP) and the overall accrued debt to 60 percent of GDP.\par \par \uc2 The draft presented on Friday proposes a \b \highlight22\uc2 deficit\b0 \highlight\uc2  of 2.53 percent of GDP and a gross-debt-to-GDP ratio of just below 39 percent.\par \par \uc2 Meanwhile, for its \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  assumptions that are part of the \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  plan, the government projects \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  growth of 5.2 percent in 2025, the same level set for this year--but a question mark hangs over this projection given the persisting global \b \highlight22\uc2 economic uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2 .\par \par \uc2 The \uc2 International Monetary Fund\uc2  and the \uc2 World Bank\uc2  both forecast that Indonesia's \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  will only grow by 5.1 percent next year.\par \par \uc2 For this year, the two project GDP of only 5 percent, below the government's 5.2 percent estimate.\par \par \uc2 Large parts of the proposed \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  for next year remain \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertain\b0 \highlight\uc2  as the plan fails to specify allocations for many \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  posts. Some might find that concerning.\par \par \uc2 However, Finance Minister \uc2 Sri Mulyani Indrawati\uc2  has pointed out that this is a transitional \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2 , and that many aspects will have to wait for answers from those who will sit in the next administration, which will depend on what Prabowo wants to pursue.\par \par \uc2 Be that as it may, we should remind Prabowo that global \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2  will persist at least until next year, and the country will need all the support it can get from the \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal\b0 \highlight\uc2  side to keep the wheels running for domestic \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  activity even in the face of potentially weak demand for Indonesian export goods.\par \par \uc2 There are hopes of interest rate cuts, but it would not be enough to undo the pain caused over the past two years as the "higher for longer" monetary \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  spearheaded by the \uc2 United States Federal Reserve\uc2  has left its mark.\par \par \uc2 We know that Prabowo may want to kick-start a lot of his campaign promises as soon as possible but we urge the president-elect to do what he must to safeguard the \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2 , before working down his own to-do list.\par \par \uc2 For those campaign promises apt to boost \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  growth to compensate for external weakness, by all means, go ahead. The key is to calibrate \b \highlight22\uc2 budget policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  in response to global and domestic developments by providing as much \b \highlight22\uc2 stimulus\b0 \highlight\uc2  as is needed but not so much as to undermine \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal\b0 \highlight\uc2  prudence and stability.\par \par \uc2 Navigating next year would also prove tricky, given that Prabowo will inherit both blessings and curses from the current administration.\par \par \uc2 President Jokowi has left many tasks unfinished, such as a planned value-added \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  (VAT) hike to 12 percent and an excise on plastics and sweetened beverages. Some of those initiatives can be instrumental in boosting revenue and keeping a lid on the \b \highlight22\uc2 deficit\b0 \highlight\uc2 , but not without side effects.\par \par \uc2 Let alone much of the past \b \highlight22\uc2 spending\b0 \highlight\uc2  with long-lasting impacts on the state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2 , including the future capital city of Nusantara's development and the \b \highlight22\uc2 deficit\b0 \highlight\uc2  from the Jakarta-Bandung high-speed railway, Whoosh, among other projects.\par \par \uc2 Some of these tasks will present tough choices for Prabowo between pursuing his own priorities and following through on legacy projects. Each of those choices must be guided by an assessment of the national interest, and that alone.\par \par \uc2 For now, there is only so much President Jokowi can do in this transition period; the \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  will need to accept unsatisfactory answers provided by the incumbent administration on \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  policies.\par \par \uc2 It remains to be seen whether the incoming administration can live up to its vows of \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal\b0 \highlight\uc2  prudence.\par \par \uc2 Next year will be the beginning for Prabowo, but only time will tell whether it will remain that way. The next administration would need to prove throughout its whole five-year term that such hard-fought prudence is something that the country can keep.\par \par \uc2 Document JKPOST0020240818ek8j0000d\par }\page {\par\fs20\uc2 Business\par \b \uc2 PDI-P Warns Gov't Against Overestimating Rupiah Depreciation in 2025  \highlight22\uc2 Budget \highlight\b0\par\par\uc2 300 \uc2 words\par \uc2 20 August 2024\par \uc2 The Jakarta Globe\par \uc2 JGLOBE\par \uc2 English\par \uc2 Copyright 2024. PT Jakarta Globe Media. \par \par \uc2 Jakarta. The Indonesian Democratic Party of Struggle (PDI-P) faction has urged the government to reconsider its macroeconomic assumptions regarding the rupiah's exchange rate. In the 2025 state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  draft (RAPBN), the rupiah is projected at Rp 16,100 per US dollar, a figure deemed inconsistent with global \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  conditions.\par \par \uc2 "The assumption of the rupiah does not align with our efforts to strengthen the currency and the global trend of monetary easing expected in 2025," said Adisatrya Suryo Sulisto, a member of the \b \highlight22\uc2 House of Representatives\b0 \highlight\uc2  (DPR) from the PDI-P faction, during a plenary session on Tuesday.\par \par \uc2 Adisatrya pointed out that the rupiah has already returned to around Rp 15,000 per US dollar. However, the government has set the 2025 exchange rate assumption at Rp 16,100 per US dollar, which contradicts the agreement between the government and the DPR when drafting the 2025 Macro \b \highlight22\uc2 Economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  Framework and \b \highlight22\uc2 Fiscal Policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  Principles (KEM PPKF), where the rupiah was estimated to range between Rp 15,300 and Rp 15,900 per US dollar.\par \par \uc2 "Therefore, the PDI-P faction believes the government should revert to the KEM PPKF agreement," Adisatrya said.\par \par \uc2 Meanwhile, Vera Febyanthy, a DPR member from the Democratic Party faction, said that the government must anticipate the impact of global \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  conditions on the stability of the rupiah. She noted that the \uc2 US Federal Reserve\uc2 's (The Fed) \b \highlight22\uc2 interest rates\b0 \highlight\uc2  remain high, which could lead to capital outflows from developing countries, affecting exchange rate stability.\par \par \uc2 "The Democratic Party faction believes that the government and \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2  should remain vigilant about global \b \highlight22\uc2 economic uncertainties\b0 \highlight\uc2 , particularly the still-high Fed \b \highlight22\uc2 interest rates\b0 \highlight\uc2 , as well as geopolitical situations that could impact the exchange rate in 2025," she said.\par \par \uc2 Document JGLOBE0020240820ek8k00008\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw177\pich40\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal2655\pichgoal600
